189
00:15:27,830 --> 00:15:31,240
He is pushing your departure
in order to show the whole world...

190
00:15:32,500 --> 00:15:35,340
that you have become his servant.

191
00:15:35,909 --> 00:15:36,940
That is right.

192
00:15:39,610 --> 00:15:42,009
