Thanks to him, we survived.

283
00:22:25,779 --> 00:22:27,720
But your father was caught.

284
00:22:36,130 --> 00:22:37,430
After catching him,

285
00:22:39,029 --> 00:22:42,200
the intruders got mad,
saying he was just a weak, old man...

286
